                <mxCell id="43" value="&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;Vous devez traverser vers un point&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;plus&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background: initial; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;près de&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;l'objectif. Mais vous devez sacrifier un de vos&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;&quot;&gt;coéquipiers pour traverser. Lequel choisirez-vous?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="rhombus;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
